
- config.h
    asciimaton configuration (paths, pins, timeouts, etc...)

- algo_img2txt.[hc]
    image to text algorithm

- algo_txt2img.[hc]
    text to image converter

- pgm.[hc]
    pgm file input/output

- txt.[hc]
    txt file input/output

- io.[hc]
    io layer for buttons/leds (supports either tty or gpio)

- weighter.c
    tool to convert font.pgm to a C array of weights for each character

- fonter.c
    tool to convert font.pgm to a C array of pixels for each character

- print.cpp
    standalone tool to print text files

- txt2img.{h,cpp}
    wrapper for algo_txt2img
    also contains standalone tool that converts txt to pgm

- img2txt.{h,cpp}
    wrapper for algo_img2txt
    also contains standalone tool that converts pgm to txt

- lp.{h,cpp}
    function to print txt data with ESC-P

- cp.{h,cpp}
    function to copy tex file

- asciimaton.cpp
    main program
